channel.title: Wot do i do!?!11one1
channel.description:
k well ive been computer geek/pro gamer for years now, many years. Had many computers, fixed many, broke many and im pro @ windows.
Now my problem is, even though my computer is pretty leet as it is now, every bit of money i get, i wanna fuckin spend it on the pc to make it even better even though it runs every game in my res and at nice settings perfect.
Specs:
22" Samsung 2243BW (i dont even know why i brought this a month ago, i have a 17" and i had 300bucks to spend on computer so i thought id buy a 2nd lcd and use 2. shove msn/irc/media player over on the 17" while i play crysis n shit on the main one.
2GB ballistix tracers 1066mhz 5-5-5-15 (yes the ones with the LEDs cuz pro gamers need lights rite?) 8800GT 500gb + 640gig HDD (640 was just cuz my mate sent me it full of warez from america, aus internet cant do shit u no) intel P35 mobo (gr8 overclocker) some random cool looking neon case 4 pro gamers some shit mouse for now, G15 keyboard, G51 speakers, and a dead G5 mouse <3 logitech.
anyway.. so like my problem is, everytime i get cash i always wanna spend it on my pc, when i could spend it on my car n clothes n shit.. its like i fuckin have to update my comp all the time (huge hobbie)
I'm gettin like 400$ soon.. and i got this fucking thing inside me, that wants to go sell my 22" monitor so ill have like 650$ to go buy a 4870x2 (those things make me so fkin hard) and if i do get that, ill need to go fuckin upgrade my PSU to at least a 800w which is another 200$ gone.
ITZ KILLIN MEH.. I GOT NO JOB OR NOTHIN N LIKE I SPEND ALL MY MONY ON SHIT, LAST WEEK PARENTS WENT ON HOLIDAY N LEFT ME 100$ FOR FOODS, BUT LEIK I SPEND 80 ON THE RAM AND TRIED TO LIVE OFF 20, WHICH 10 WENT TO MACCAS ON THE FIRST DAY.
halp plx? // oh i also whats pissin me off, is like i got fkin 50 games or some shit on my pc.. yet i play none of them (css/crysis a lil bit) like i dont even use my pc much for what its meant for, i just browse internet and chat on irc/bot some rsc clients/listen music/watch movies.
